<p> </p>
<p>Above are some photos from the 2nd edition of the French MarkLogic User Group, held last Tuesday in Paris. Thirty-five people gathered to discuss MarkLogic implementation examples as part of a series of four presentations.  The <a href="http://www.mug-fr.org/2010/12/conference-1-ron-avnur-fonctionnalites-marklogic-server-et-cas-d%E2%80%99utilisation/">first presentation</a> was done by Ron Avnur, MarkLogic VP of Engineering, who was attending his first MarkLogic User Group. Ron presented a sample of MarkLogic customer use cases as well as some of the latest MarkLogic Server features. </p>
