<p> </p>
<p>The <a href="http://www.mug-fr.org/2010/12/conference-2-vincent-mas-presentation-du-projet-digital-factory-base-sur-marklogic/">second presentation</a> was done by Vincent MAS from <a href="http://www.lagardere.com/activites/lagardere-active-2610.html">Lagardere Active</a>. He presented the Digital Factory project, a highly interesting MarkLogic implementation. We had the chance to view and hear some unique archives such as Appollo 11 landing on the Moon.</p>
