<p> </p>
<p>The <a href="http://www.mug-fr.org/2010/12/conference-3-gregory-corona-presentation-d%E2%80%99un-demonstrateur-de-geolocalisation-base-sur-l%E2%80%99api-%C2%AB-geospacial-%C2%BB-de-marklogic-server/">third presentation</a> was done by Gregory CORONA and Yoann BLOT from <a href="http://www.4dconcept.fr/">4Dconcept</a>. They presented GeoLab, a prototype that implements MarkLogic's geospatial functionnality. GeoLab prooves by A+B that geospatial query are easy and powerful to perform with MarkLogic, even with a fully custom-made search area such as a polygone. The use-case is based on the well-known Tour de France.</p>
